OL,5, A wrongly jailed former sub-postmaster 
OL,6, says a new TV drama about the Horizon  
OL,7, Post Office scandal is important in    
OL,8, getting the story to a wider audience. 
OL,10,FNoel Thomas, 77, from Anglesey, was one
OL,11,Fof more than 700 convicted in the      
OL,12,Fmiscarriage of justice.                
OL,14,F"I think it's going to bring it home   
OL,15,Ffor a lot of people," said the man sent
OL,16,Fto prison for false accounting in 2006,
OL,17,Fwhose conviction was quashed in 2021.  
OL,19,FITV's Mr Bates vs The Post Office tells
OL,20,Fthe tale of the lives that were ruined.
